*''[[They Don't Wear Black Tie]]'' (1981)
*''[[Quilombo (film)|Quilombo]]'' (1984)
*''[[Love Me Forever or Never]]'' (1986)
*''[[Ironweed (film)|Ironweed]]'' (1987)
*''[[At Play in the Fields of the Lord]]'' (1991)
*''[[Amelia Earhart: The Final Flight]]'' (1994)
*''[[Foolish Heart (1998 film)|Foolish Heart]]'' (1998)
*''[[A Hidden Life (2001 film)|A Hidden Life]]'' (2001)
*''[[Maids (film)|Maids]]'' (2001)
*''[[A Samba for Sherlock]]'' (2001)
*''[[The Greatest Love of All (film)|The Greatest Love of All]]'' (2006)
*''[[Baptism of Blood]]'' (2006)
*''[[Casa da Mãe Joana]]'' (2008)
*''[[O Contador de Histórias]]'' (2009)
*''[[Casa da Mãe Joana 2]]'' (2013)

